snippet.title: Best VGM 833 - Trauma Team - Anyway Let's Begin The Diagnosis
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo Wii
Trauma Team (2010)
Anyway Let's Begin The Diagnosis
Ryota Koduka
